<p><strong></strong>Welcome to <strong>Sprint #3</strong> of <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/events/293162500/">Intro to Software Development</a></strong>.</p>
<p><strong>Scorecard</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong>~ Eight members signed up for Intro to Software Development<br />~ Three members made the commitment to begin<br />~ Two members completed Sprint #1<br />~ Zero members completed Sprint #2</p>
<p><strong>Next Steps</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong>This Third sprint will last one week and will cover the third of three courses in <strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/learning/paths/career-essentials-in-software-development-by-microsoft-and-linkedin">Career Essentials in Software Development by Microsoft and LinkedIn</a></strong>—a LinkedIn Learning Path. Once you log into your LinkedIn account, you have <strong>FREE</strong> access to this six-hour, three-course certificate program.</p>
<p>By now you should have posted a brief update to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53875156">Introduce Yourself</a></strong> which will acknowledge your commitment to begin this training opportunity. You may begin your journey at any time. However, the first step in starting the journey is making the commitment to begin.</p>
<p><strong>Sprint 3</strong> covers <strong>Programming Foundations: Beyond the Fundamentals</strong>. This third of three sprints begins on May 29 and concludes on June 4, 2023. Once you complete this two-hour course you will receive a certificate of completion you can post to your LinkedIn profile. Please share a link to your certificate at <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53892031">Sprint 3—Intro to Software Development</a></strong> so that I can monitor participant progress. Of course, you should complete <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53879699">Sprint 1</a></strong> and <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53885363">Sprint 2</a></strong> before you move on to <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53892031">Sprint 3</a></strong>.</p>
<p>Links to all discussions are posted at <strong><a href="https://www.meetup.com/bostonphp/messages/boards/thread/53874249">Master Discussion List</a>.</strong></p>
<p>Let's keep developing.</p>
